Incorporating air quality health impacts into the social cost of carbon
                    Cora Kingdon 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-6207-10481, Kevin R. Cromar 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-7745-27802,3, Susan C. Anenberg 
